39 premiums is adequate to pay for expected losses, expenses and
40 taxes;
41 (c) Reflect the investment income of the FAIR Plan; and
42 (d) Reflect the cost of reinsurance or other capital risk transfer
43 markets.
44 3. All rate filing documentation and review requirements set
